<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="locate-vt">locate <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ləʊ'keɪt/    美 /'loʊkeɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>找出…的位置：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Because of their small size and sharp sense of smell, dogs can locate survivors much faster than humans can.
由于体形小、嗅觉敏锐，狗能比人类更快地找到幸存者。</p><footer>译林新必修③ – 2</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>把…设置 (在)；使…坐落 (于)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The company located its branch office in the suburbs.
这家公司在郊区设立了办事处。</p></div></div>